## Description {#details}

A container for string pool string values.

This class is used with the DW&#95;FORM&#95;strp and DW&#95;FORM&#95;GNU&#95;str&#95;index forms.

Definition at line 278 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/die-h">DIE.h</a>.
